<h1>烧</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">shāo</span><span class=alesi>(shao1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 烧 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 烧</h2><div class=abo>
